text: Hermann von Siebenthal (27 December 1934 - 31 March 2014) was a Swiss equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics
